- Improve performance on Windows especially for non-Latin scripts
- Bugs fixed:
    Bug 628497 - Crash in pango_layout_line_get_extents at pango-layout.c
    Bug 626966 - SIGFPE _hb_sanitize_array
    Bug 629632 - configure bug
